    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "With the merger of IE Singapore and the Standards, Productivity and Innovation Board (SPRING Singapore) in April 2018, the Enterprise Singapore Board is now the regulatory body responsible for administering the CTA."
